-- Synovus Financial Chairman-CEO Anthony to Take Medical Leave of Absence
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-06-21T13:13:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/synovus-financial-chairman-ceo-anthony-to-take-medical-leave-of-absence.html

          
          
             Synovus Financial Corp. said Richard
E. Anthony, chief executive officer and chairman, will take a
medical leave of absence, effective immediately.  
 The board named Kessel D. Stelling, Jr., current president
and chief operating officer, as acting CEO.  
          
          


  


        